    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2 due to single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol; this gap is accepted given the conservative nature of the single test condition, the medium model influence, and corroborating experimental data from two independent laboratories. Quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all three primary QoIs. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
